Solve sudokus by using a backtracking algorithm
===============================================

compile the program by running make

write your sudoku in a file using the following format:

---39--1-
5-1----4-
9--7--5--
6-253--7-
----7---8
7--8--9-3
8-3-1--9-
-9-2-6--7
4----3-61

the '-' character represents a not known number
all other numbers are the known numbers

then solve the sudoku:

./sudoku mysudoku.txt
